Title: Relates to signatures for designating petitions for political subdivisions outside the city of New York
Summary: Relates to signatures for designating petitions for political subdivisions outside the city of New York; must be signed by not less than three and three-quarters per centum.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the election law, in relation to signatures for designating petitions for political subdivisions outside the city of New York; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
